{"tid":1394781,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[遍地開花] 8.11文宣 深水埗接力開花","createTime":"2019-08-01T14:03:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T17:02:03.000Z","uid":64538,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e69762805ae1de6487691b9a39c022585896e0f0","tid":1394781,"uid":64538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:03:22.000Z","msg":"除咗8.5大罷工 依家<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">深水埗區</span></span>接力開花<br />\n大家可能開始覺得攰 但係唔好放棄<br />\n我地有45個手足被捕 前線勇武受傷<br />\n我地因而更加要出黎聲援佢地 亦都要呢個政府聆聽我地嘅訴求<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\n可能有啲係自己一個出 驚尷尬<br />\n但唔洗驚 因為我地有千千萬萬個陪你<br />\n所以<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 唔該大家8.11 一齊行出黎 </span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QZshYvr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQZshYvr.png&h=30fc6233&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DPT85at.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDPT85at.png&h=39b07b86&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rULb2W9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrULb2W9.png&h=eae1ac28&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CMLzgha.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCMLzgha.png&h=0e7ff3af&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EOheghb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEOheghb.png&h=3e57da3b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BvCFbQw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBvCFbQw.png&h=fd4b839e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gBiH9Cc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgBiH9Cc.png&h=e80f2294&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EHnhYvy.png\" data-thumbn